Sales Cloud has a fresh look in new Salesforce orgs. The streamlined color palette, font, and spacing improvements, with the increased contrast, help you find and focus on the information that matters most to you.

This change applies to Sales Cloud Professional and Enterprise editions.

The enhanced Lightning user interface is available in new Sales Cloud Professional Edition orgs created after June 27, 2024, and in new Sales Cloud Enterprise Edition orgs created after July 25, 2024.

If the original Lightning Experience is preferred or if themes and customizations are needed, you can opt out of the enhanced Lightning user interface by turning it off in User Interface Settings in Setup.

Financial Services Cloud is currently not compatible with the enhanced Lightning user interface.
title: Enhanced Lightning UI in Sales Cloud
